column5: Is there any reports off greenbacks in the Red. If so, where is the action and the bait of choice. Feedback is would very helpfull because I have to stay close to home this weekend and don't want to make it a total waste of time. Thanks.

Just got another report on Fishing MB board someone got a 7 1/2 lb just north of Lockport. There are the odd ones being caught.I m stuck here working. Who cares if only the odd one is about, just go fishing,it still beats sittin around the houseWWhttp://www.walleyewarrior.com
